These drugs have demonstrated exceptional average performance, where performance is measured by Mahalanobis distance; 
They have been extensively studied, as indicated by a large total sample size; 
They have garnered significant funding, represented by total funding received.

sql:
SELECT drug_id, AVG(mahalanobis_dist) AS avg_mahalanobis_distance
FROM drug_metrics
GROUP BY drug_id;

SELECT drug_name
FROM drugs
WHERE status = 'approved' AND molecular_weight > (SELECT AVG(molecular_weight) FROM drugs);
